{"tid":1649024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奧斯卡影帝Michael Douglas 狠批香港《反蒙面法》愚蠢","createTime":"2019-10-12T13:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T15:05:40.000Z","uid":134071,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9298b72450f1bf18baeba90271f9f642fdbd74b5","tid":1649024,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191012/60142851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60142851&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9pzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=ecda9575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60142851&h=c2150597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191012/60142851</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年10月12日<br />\n【獨家專訪】影帝米高德格拉斯密謀選總統 狠批香港蒙面惡法很愚蠢 <br />\n<br />\n現年75歲的奧斯卡金像影帝米高德格拉斯（Michael Douglas），今年憑他主演的Netflix出品電視劇《荷里活教父》（The Kominsky Method）在金球獎勇奪喜劇組視帝，趁住該劇第二季即將上架，米高德格拉斯近日在比華利山四季酒店接受《蘋果》獨家專訪。<br />\n<br />\n《荷里活教父》描述一名演藝導師Sandy和他經理人Norman之間的故事，昨年Netflix推出第一季時已好評如潮，繼揚威金球獎後，也獲提名多項艾美獎，今季故事更加精采，也請了多位巨星客串演出。<strong>米高德格拉斯日前接受訪問，他在過程中對香港近況表現關心，特地向香港市民送上祝福，並希望大家平安，當得知香港政府以《緊急法》來訂立《反蒙面法》，他不禁批評做法並不合理，還說：「政府嚴禁示威者戴上面罩，做法真的很愚蠢。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實，米高德格拉斯與家人曾先後多次訪港，難怪對香港目前情況及前途十分關心。同時，米高太太嘉芙蓮薛達鍾絲（Catherine Zeta-Jones）去年曾暗示丈夫有意競選美國總統，而米高曾於1995年電影《白宮奇緣》（The American President）中演過總統，隨時加入總統之戰與特朗普（Donald Trump）爭做總統。<br />\n<br />\n談到從影以來，於80年代演出及製作了很多部精采電影，他說：「是的，我在80年代和90年代很成功，拍了很多部電影如《飛越瘋人院》（One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest）、《本能》（The Basic Instinct）、《孽緣》（Fatal Attraction）、《華爾街金融大鱷》（Wall Street: Money Never Sleeps）等，之後我也開了一間製作公司，開始監製的工作，我很愛監製的工作，但好的劇本實在不多，於是我決定留在家中跟子女們生活，在我上一段婚姻我常去了拍戲，所以長子Cameron也出了很多問題，所以我現在非常之挑剔，現在只拍《荷里活教父》。」"},{"pid":"6d9a8358b16a89dc298936e31e8c42b16fa252c0","tid":1649024,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"諗起1992年有兩大色情片霸: 梁家輝既《情人》同Michael Douglas既《本能》.  當時我已經覺得Michael Douglas完勝梁家輝, 事實證明我無睇錯人! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/KrX4Bo8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrX4Bo8.jpg&h=e2d64042&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29b3ea36bb5321d52688d328f91bfc4681063b5d","tid":1649024,"uid":80277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b388bd2a66cefb62570d72057a97e23331f6a153","tid":1649024,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:04:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"224bfbb16a3d42a512b6d17bc166f0710440bd27","tid":1649024,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"小支支幾時ban哂成個荷李活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cb922f022c6905b10dea52856771a4a0ab691f","tid":1649024,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"Michael Douglas都係Marvel演員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uaz6nxyQA28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Duaz6nxyQA28&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9pzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=734070d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uaz6nxyQA28</a>"},{"pid":"9321f91f924cac3ab2a24140b601a93eadbdf65e","tid":1649024,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB