代演出及製作了很多部精采電影，他說：「是的，我在80年代和90年代很成功，拍了很多部電影如《飛越瘋人院》（One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest）、《本能》（The Basic Instinct）、《孽緣》（Fatal Attraction）、《華爾街金融大鱷》（Wall Street: Money Never Sleeps）等，之後我也開了一間製作公司，開始監製的工作，我很愛監製的工作，但好的劇本實在不多，於是我決定留在家中跟子女們生活，在我上一段婚姻我常去了拍戲，所以長子Cameron也出了很多問題，所以我現在非常之挑剔，現在只拍《荷里活教父》。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:16:04.000Z","msg":"[行動POST] 想要靚畫面？銀髮族48小時靜坐咪就係機會囉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648992</a><br />\n<br />\n警總靜坐現場，有老人有中年人有外國人有後生仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多中年帶哂席同櫈黎，準備過夜。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">想有新行動？想要靚畫面？咁你就快啲過黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日攰唔出都唔緊要，準備聽日接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我煲大佢，唔好當銀髮手足係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAwXWg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAwXWg8.jpg&h=aab0f8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3c9e56de4937246851c828cd5c15b7989112c9e","tid":1649024,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黎緊10 14一次過多謝哂美國關心香港事務既人啦<br />\nmorey 一定要多謝"},{"pid":"5536e17afc48e1d090c175d3b9d546fc7faf831c","tid":1649024,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d7b66a6aca0fa1213e2b13024b9a09d5c8c411","tid":1649024,"uid":59633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"Hank Pym<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abb667149f7c046bf4cab16de9f091f3e027ff5","tid":1649024,"uid":276715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"Thank you, sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ab345f78e5d5cb65b7574ecfc7a6c024add2a8","tid":1649024,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"Thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}